TopicTitle: KSP crashes laptop when in VAB

Articles.Content:
KSP has been consistently crashing my laptop (hard lock/BSOD) with a video scheduler error whenever I'm in the VAB, so it's basically unplayable.

I've noticed that the error log (copied below) seems to suggest that KSP is using the integrated Intel HD graphics adaptor, rather than my NVidia card (despite being set to do so in the NVidia manager). Could that be the problem?
